    "note": "Extension convention for N64 saves: .eep=EEPROM, .sra=SRAM, .fla=Flash RAM. The .n64 extension is sometimes used for complete save state snapshots. N64 game cartridges contain a string 'EEPROM', 'SRAM', or 'FLASH' identifying the save type."
  },
